        <div class="text-center mt-2 mb-4 text-ink/40" style="font-size: 0.75rem;">Edge estimate error (%)</div>

        <figcaption class="mb-8">Figure 3 - Long-run growth rate when the gambler's edge estimate is wrong. Half Kelly stays positive across a much wider error range.</figcaption>
      </div>

      <div class="readout-grid" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;" id="s4-stats">
